The rule is for every 100 imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.001
Total buy share: 0
Total sell share: 38
Imbalance: -38
Multiplier: 0.99962

21.18.44 10-02-25
Algorithm 2: Order Imbalance: buy vs sell demand in term of order amount
Stock symbol: ADBE
The rule is for every total order amount, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.01
Total buy orders: 0
Total sell orders: 2
Imbalance: -2
Multiplier: 0.99

21.18.44 10-02-25
Algorithm 3: Cumulative Order Book Depth: buy vs sell demand in term of price level
Stock symbol: ADBE
The rule is for every 50 imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.01
Total buy share: 0
Total sell share: 29
Imbalance: -29
Multiplier: 0.9942

21.18.44 10-02-25
Algorithm 4: Market Pressure from Large Orders (Iceberg Effect): buy vs sell in term of largest share of buy/sell orders that deviate from the current stock price
Stock symbol: ADBE
The rule is for every 15 large order imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.05
Average buy share: 0
Average sell share: 19
Large amount threashold: 9
Number of large buy orders: 0
Number of large sell orders: 1
Imbalance: -1
Multiplier: 0.9986666666666667

21.18.44 10-02-25
Algorithm 5: Order Flow Momentum: check the recent 5 seconds time window of buy/sell orders, and if there is a momentum in the order flow, then increase/decrease the stock price perspectively
Stock symbol: ADBE
The rule is for every 10 recent order imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.1
Recent buy orders: 0
Recent sell orders: 0
Imbalance: 0
Multiplier: 1

21.18.44 10-02-25

The rule is for every 100 imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.001
Total buy share: 115
Total sell share: 0
Imbalance: 115
Multiplier: 1.00115

21.18.48 10-02-25
Algorithm 2: Order Imbalance: buy vs sell demand in term of order amount
Stock symbol: GOOGL
The rule is for every total order amount, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.01
Total buy orders: 1
Total sell orders: 0
Imbalance: 1
Multiplier: 1.01

21.18.48 10-02-25
Algorithm 3: Cumulative Order Book Depth: buy vs sell demand in term of price level
Stock symbol: GOOGL
The rule is for every 50 imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.01
Total buy share: 115
Total sell share: 0
Imbalance: 115
Multiplier: 1.023

21.18.48 10-02-25
Algorithm 4: Market Pressure from Large Orders (Iceberg Effect): buy vs sell in term of largest share of buy/sell orders that deviate from the current stock price
Stock symbol: GOOGL
The rule is for every 15 large order imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.05
Average buy share: 115
Average sell share: 0
Large amount threashold: 57
Number of large buy orders: 1
Number of large sell orders: 0
Imbalance: 1
Multiplier: 1.0013333333333334

21.18.48 10-02-25
Algorithm 5: Order Flow Momentum: check the recent 5 seconds time window of buy/sell orders, and if there is a momentum in the order flow, then increase/decrease the stock price perspectively
Stock symbol: GOOGL
The rule is for every 10 recent order imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.1
Recent buy orders: 0
Recent sell orders: 0
Imbalance: 0
Multiplier: 1

21.18.48 10-02-25

The rule is for every 100 imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.001
Total buy share: 95
Total sell share: 63
Imbalance: 32
Multiplier: 1.00032

21.18.50 10-02-25
Algorithm 2: Order Imbalance: buy vs sell demand in term of order amount
Stock symbol: GILD
The rule is for every total order amount, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.01
Total buy orders: 1
Total sell orders: 1
Imbalance: 0
Multiplier: 1

21.18.50 10-02-25
Algorithm 3: Cumulative Order Book Depth: buy vs sell demand in term of price level
Stock symbol: GILD
The rule is for every 50 imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.01
Total buy share: 95
Total sell share: 63
Imbalance: 32
Multiplier: 1.0064

21.18.50 10-02-25
Algorithm 4: Market Pressure from Large Orders (Iceberg Effect): buy vs sell in term of largest share of buy/sell orders that deviate from the current stock price
Stock symbol: GILD
The rule is for every 15 large order imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.05
Average buy share: 95
Average sell share: 63
Large amount threashold: 79
Number of large buy orders: 1
Number of large sell orders: 0
Imbalance: 1
Multiplier: 1.0013333333333334

21.18.50 10-02-25
Algorithm 5: Order Flow Momentum: check the recent 5 seconds time window of buy/sell orders, and if there is a momentum in the order flow, then increase/decrease the stock price perspectively
Stock symbol: GILD
The rule is for every 10 recent order imbalance, the stock price will increase/decrease by 0.1
Recent buy orders: 0
Recent sell orders: 0
Imbalance: 0
Multiplier: 1

21.18.50 10-02-25
